  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="1493576">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/1493576/" class="title-link">绞肉机</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-1493576"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/2899061/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2899061-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/2899061/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">末日咆哮</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2008-09-10"
      class="main-meta">2008-09-10 15:04:59</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_1493576_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  苏德版本的都不好，大概是因为当年的政治格局所至，内容都很片面，甚至有很大程度的水分。还是英美作家的作品比较好，角度客观。 斯大林格勒保卫战可以算是人类有史以来最惨烈的一场战役，那里的每一存土地都浸满了鲜血，就算是没有亲历过那场绝世之战的人们，光从触目惊心的伤...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">1有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_1493576_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_1493576_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评1篇
                </a>
            </p>
</section>
    
